#!/usr/bin/env python3
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
# Problem:
# https://cses.fi/problemset/task/1080
# Author:
# https://cses.fi/users/janne
# Date:
# 2019-12-19

import sys

def main():
    n, m = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
    days = 0
    while n > 0:
        if n >= m:
            n -= m
        else:
            n = 0
        days += 1
    print(days)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
